  ('generalpolice-f3743df6-moex-00094', 'generalpolice-f3743df6', 'generalpolice-f3743df6-moex-113-bb28a373', 'sub-generalpolice-f3743df6-04', NULL, 'essay', '甲持有小客車駕駛執照，受僱於乙物流公司載運貨物。一日乙公司之大
